data.description: Discover the allure of this expansive residence nestled against a backdrop of a lush greenbelt! Step into a 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom haven featuring an inviting open-concept kitchen and living space, complemented by a dedicated office area. Outside, a meticulously maintained yard invites you to unwind in style. Embrace the generous proportions of each bedroom, ensuring ample space for comfort. This residence effortlessly combines modern aesthetics with natural charm, offering a lifestyle that goes beyond the ordinary.
